{"tid":755953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有木蝨 點氹掂老母dum曬啲無用嘢","createTime":"2018-07-25T15:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T00:07:24.000Z","uid":196743,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5eb7d31fddd76bc358516db65a90f75623f1a7","tid":755953,"uid":196743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"我老母好撚鍾意收收埋埋啲無用嘅嘢 搞到成屋雜物 <br />\n本身都諗住算 老人家鍾意都無辦法 <br />\n<br />\n屌 但係今年夏天屋企又出返啲木蝨 （本身前年夏天都有）<br />\n把心一橫諗住換撚曬我間房啲床呀櫃呀枱呀 <br />\n唉但係諗諗下 淨係換自己個啲無用 <br />\n可能隔多排啲木蝨又入返黎我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係好想清潔呀！！但咁撚多雜物 點清呀！！<br />\n有冇人可以教下我點做<br />\n<br />\nbtw我老母係好硬頸個啲人嚟 永遠唔聽人講嘢 <br />\n即使佢俾木蝨咬 都係見到一隻捉一隻 冇諗住要做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d51f22deaadedce3c41630eb20a061d688eef70","tid":755953,"uid":6250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"搵滅蟲啦<br />\n最近先搵完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76742bcdb04742bf4265c9f586f436a9cfdacbc4","tid":755953,"uid":126695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"dum咗自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58387d2cb7dbd2a719552b58f245ded0ee7cae63","tid":755953,"uid":196743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d51f22deaadedce3c41630eb20a061d688eef70","tid":755953,"uid":6250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"搵滅蟲啦<br />\n最近先搵完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"有用緊de粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似清唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n搵滅蟲但屋企咁多雜物清唔清到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9fc769cf887af436f0290b5ca8c2c02e2182a7","tid":755953,"ui